description: Details of the laying out and finishes to hard landscape areas pursuant to condition 15 of planning permission ref: P/2012/1991 dated 27/09/2012 for Redevelopment of site to provide a part two, three and four storey 8 form entry secondary school with 6th. form and SEN accommodation, with vehicular and pedestrian access off Oldfield Lane North , car park and cycle storage areas, provision of sports pitches (including floodlit multi use games areas and other all weather surfaces, hard and soft landscaping (including mound and swale along the A40 frontage)
